or percentages -&gt; Save[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title=\"How to disable breadcrumbs?\"][vc_column_text]Please follow Theme Options -&gt; Page titles -&gt; Breadcrumbs -&gt; Disable -&gt; Save[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title=\"How many slideshows am I able to create?\"][vc_column_text]You are able to create as many slideshows as you want and use them on any page or post.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title=\"What cache plugin do you suggest to use?\"][vc_column_text]We would like to advise you to install <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/plugins/w3-total-cache/\" target=\"_blank\">W3 Total Cache</a> plugin.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title=\"Can I use Widgets in Visual Composer?\"][vc_column_text]Yes, you can ad widget areas with the help of Widgetised Sidebar shortcode.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title=\"How to change the number of columns in footer?\"][vc_column_text]Please follow Theme Options -&gt; General -&gt; Footer &amp; Bottom Bar -&gt; Footer -&gt; Footer Layout -&gt; Layout -&gt; Enter the desired footer structure, f.e. 1/2+1/4+1/4 -&gt; Save[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title=\"How can I activate Slider Revolution?\"][vc_column_text]The notice about Slider Revolution registration is a suggestion, not a requirement.\n\nThe plugin is registered on Dream-Theme, and buyers of this theme do not need to register it once again. So, for now, could you please simply disregard the notice.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title=\"How to remove a gap between slideshow and content?\"][vc_column_text]There are 50px gaps between header and content area, content area and footer. You can add negative top and bottom margins (-50) in Visual Composer row setting to remove these gaps.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title=\"Submit your question!\"][vc_empty_space height=\"10px\"][dt_co